ABOUT
A Local Legend Since 2006
From its opening on Sanford’s birthday, September 29, 2006, West End Trading Co. has been a cornerstone of the Historic Downtown Sanford community. Starting as a cozy dive bar, we've evolved into a bustling venue that features some of the best live music and entertainment in Central Florida.

Over the years, we've hosted iconic events like the Hurricane Party Concert, built the legendary Fishbowl Stage, and created our signature drink, the Sunshine State Bomb, enjoyed by over a million guests.
Unrivaled Entertainment
From live bands and DJs to karaoke nights, there’s always a reason to come back.
A Local Touch
We proudly represent Sanford, offering a warm, hometown vibe.
Top-Notch Service
Our team is passionate about making your experience memorable.
Unbeatable Happy Hour
Enjoy our famous Happy Hour every day of the week—because good times should never break the bank!
Live Music Experience
Catch incredible performances from local, regional, and national acts at West End Live, our professional music venue.
Delicious Bites
From Cosmic Wings to classic bar bites, The Joint serves up mouthwatering flavors that are the perfect companion to any night out.
Community Connection
West End is more than a bar—it’s a hub for local events, a supporter of community causes, and a place where everyone feels like family.
Rooted in Sanford
West End Trading Co. is more than a bar—it’s a gathering place where Sanford comes together to celebrate, connect, and thrive.
Community
Where It Began
From humble beginnings to hosting legendary events, West End’s history is woven into the fabric of Historic Downtown Sanford.
History
Green initiatives
Committed to a
Sustainable Future
At West End Trading Co., we believe in doing our part to protect the planet. With solar panels now up and running, we're reducing our carbon footprint and harnessing clean energy. We also prioritize recycling, ensuring that cardboard, cans, and plastics are properly disposed of. Our next step? We're looking into composting as part of our ongoing efforts to create a greener, more sustainable Earth for future generations.

We’d Love to Hear From You!
Whether you have a question, want to book an event, or simply want to drop by for a drink, we’re here to help! At West End Trading Co., we value our customers and are always happy to connect with the Sanford community. West End Events
West End Events: Live Shows & Weekly Fun
Discover the heart of Downtown Sanford's nightlife at West End Trading Co. and West End Live! From live music and DJ sets that light up the stage to our crowd-favorite weekly events, there’s always something happening. Whether you’re here for karaoke, poker, or a killer live performance, you’ll find good times, great drinks, and even better company. Check out what’s coming up and join the party!
